==Finnish==

===Derivational suffix===
'''-io''' (''with back vowel harmony'')

'''-iö''' (''with front vowel harmony'')

# Forms nouns from verbs or verbal stems.
#: [[itää]] ''to sprout'' -&gt; [[itiö]] ''spore (of eg. mushroom, moss)''
# Forms nouns from other nouns, adjectives, numbers or their stems.
#: [[tuomari]] ''judge'' -&gt; [[tuomio]] ''judgement''
#: [[kaksi]] ''two'' -&gt; [[kaksio]] ''flat (apartment) for two people''

----

==Italian==
===Suffix===
'''-io''' 

# continuation, strength
# state, condition

